'''''I'm a Teacher, Get Me Out of Here''''' is a novel by [[Francis Gilbert]]. It was first published in hardback, in 2003 by Short Books.

A parody of the TV show ''[[I'm a Celebrity...Get Me Out of Here! (UK TV series)|I'm a Celebrity...Get Me Out of Here!]]'', it is set around a teacher's trials and tribulations, in an [[inner city]] school, from training to teaching. Gilbert bases this book on his own teaching experiences, much of the content being close to fact with only names and locations changed.

Well received by critics, the novel was released in paperback in 2005 ({{ISBN|978-1904095682}}).<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/books/reviews/im-a-teacher-get-me-out-of-here-by-francis-gilbert-558543.html |title=I'm A Teacher, Get Me Out Of Here, by Francis Gilbert|location=London |work=The Independent|author=Bill Greenwell|date=2 April 2004 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20091127190940/http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/books/reviews/im-a-teacher-get-me-out-of-here-by-francis-gilbert-558543.html |archivedate=2009-11-27 |df= }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|author=Francis Gilbert |url=https://www.theguardian.com/books/2004/feb/29/biography.schools |title=I've learnt my lesson |publisher=Guardian |date=29 February 2004 |accessdate={{date| 9 dec 2014}}}}</ref><ref>[http://www.epolitix.com/mpwebsites/mparticles/mparticledetails/newsarticle/a-class-act-im-a-teacher-get-me-out-of-here-francis-gilbert-short-books///mpsite/clare-short/?no_cache=1 ] {{dead link|date=July 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|author=Mo Serruya |url=http://www.thisisull.com/reviews/books/cathyteacher.html |title=Hull Local Book Reviews - I'm a Teacher Get Me Out of Here by Francis Gilbert (Short Books) Reviewed By Cathy Walker |publisher=Thisisull.com |date={{date|07 jun 2005 }}|accessdate={{date| 9 dec 2014}}}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|author=John Mannion |url=https://www.theguardian.com/books/2004/apr/10/featuresreviews.guardianreview1 |title=Review: I'm a Teacher, Get Me Out of Here! by Francis Gilbert &#124; Books |publisher=The Guardian |date=2013-10-06 |accessdate=2013-10-12 |location=London}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Blum |first=Hester |url=http://www.accessmylibrary.com/coms2/summary_0286-21045311_ITM |title=Article: The hard school of education.(I'm A Teacher, Get Me Out Of Here)(Book... &#124; AccessMyLibrary - Promoting library advocacy |publisher=AccessMyLibrary |date= |accessdate=2013-10-12}}</ref>

