{{member|name="Anastasia" of Siberia|nota=Wilderness dweller. The subject of [[Vladimir Megre|Vladimir Nikolaevic Megre]]'s Anastasia / [http://www.ringingcedarsofrussia.org/Main/English/index.php Ringing Cedars] books, she lives in the Siberian [[taiga]] (arboreal forest), immersed in nature, amongst plants, animals, and nature spirits which provide for all her needs. After her parents' accidental deaths, she was raised by two sages, her grandfather and great-grandfather. Her story has inspired thousands to take up country living, simplicity, and nature awareness.<ref>The life and teachings of Vladimir Megre's lover "Anastasia" and of Tom Brown's mentor "Stalking Wolf" are profoundly inspiring, but the physical existence of each of these two characters has been questioned due to insufficient evidence and corroboration.</ref>|ref=[http://www.vladimirmegre.com/biography.php Vladimir Megre]}}
